      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 58</em>, <em>Adventurer's Armory pg. 19</em>, <em>PRPG Core Rulebook pg. 158</em><br/><strong>Price</strong> 2 cp; <strong>Weight</strong> 1 lb.<br/><strong>Category</strong> Adventuring Gear</p><h2 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\" title=\"PFS Legal\"/>Description</h2><p>A whetstone allows you to sharpen a blade by sliding it against the stone at a precise angle. Honing a blade with a whetstone requires about 15 minutes of work and grants the weapon a +1 bonus on your damage roll the first time you hit with it. This only works on nonmagical blades.</p>",
